
FRONT-END
1. npm install create-react-app -global
2. npx create-react-app news-app
3. cd news-app
4. npm start
5. npm install @mui/material @emotion/react @emotion/styled @mui/styled-engine-sc styled-components @mui/icons-material
6. npm install react-router-dom
7. npm install axios
8. npm install @fontsource/roboto

BACK-END
1. npm init --y
2. npm i --save json-server
3. change the line in package.json: 
      "scripts": {
        "test": "echo \"Error: no test specified\" && exit 1"
      }
  into
      "scripts": {
        "start": "json-server -p 3006 -w db.json"
      }

LOCAL STORAGE
1. save data: localStorage.setItem(key, value);
2. read data: localStorage.getItem(key);
3. remove data: localStorage.removeItem(key);
4. remove all: localStorage.clear();

JAVASCRIPT JSON 
1. convert from string to object: JSON.parse()
2. convert into string: JSON.stringify()
